name: textures
description:
"textures" is the 10th song off my new beattape "souls" releaseing August 27, 2021. i layered up some textures to create a quick beat that is pleasing to the ear and good for a background study sesh. 

the cover art was generated by AI using the text prompt "soul textures" and it came up with some waves engulfing souls. 

Bop your head and enjoy the music. If you purchase this piece, hit me up on twitter @ryanartwalker and I will send you the album with high quality AIFF files!
